flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Display Menu]
    B --> C[Accept User Input]
    C --> D{Exit?}
    D -->|Yes| E([End])
    D -->|No| F{Transformation?}
    F -->|uppercase| G[Convert to Uppercase]
    F -->|lowercase| H[Convert to Lowercase]
    F -->|reverse| I[Reverse String]
    F -->|collapse whitespace| J[Collapse Whitespace]
    G --> K[Display Result]
    H --> K
    I --> K
    J --> K
    K --> B